{"tid":1738674,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【靜過鬼】無綫電視城變空城 台慶錄影廠得孤伶伶蛋糕","createTime":"2019-11-19T10:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T08:18:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":129,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6d99f128de7e5b18c16d5e3209296f6c20146047","tid":1738674,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"逆權運動抗爭激烈，香港人反紅媒情緒高漲，遭網民譏諷為CCTVB的無綫，今日踏入52周年，惟有網民發起「全民和你賀台㷫」，有傳大台擔心被圍，所以將今晚舉行《珍惜香港 發放娛樂 TVB 52年》台慶直播節目，改為於昨日提早錄影，今日電視城變了「空城」！<br />\n<br />\n據知，聽聞今日除了《愛．回家之開心速遞》的劇組之外，所有演員都不用返電視城開工，而台慶的錄影廠空無一人，只餘下一個主景舞台，其他佈景板已全部拆除，只有一個52周年台慶蛋糕孤伶伶在台上，旁邊的化妝間都沒有人，連工作人員都沒有，整個電視城靜過鬼。<br />\n今晚台慶的司儀是汪明荃（阿姐）、鄭裕玲、陳貝兒、袁文傑、陸浩明等，阿姐回覆傳媒承認昨晚已錄影，今日不用做直播，所以阿姐不會返電視城。<br />\n<br />\n至於今晚的節目環節，包括有高海寧表演地上絲帶舞、王君馨表演鋼管舞、張曦雯表演空中瑜伽舞、周柏豪和菊梓喬合唱等，全部昨日已錄影，安排今晚播出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191119/large/1574155882_e4a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574155882_e4a5.jpg&h=55a7d5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191119/60285532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60285532&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=a411d6b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60285532&h=16c93f48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191119/60285532</a>"},{"pid":"96963f2ae13345d1fd2569a7b6f67ac03b5b6199","tid":1738674,"uid":137604,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"又話圍電視城<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"