c5400eed","tid":1738674,"uid":293673,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:35:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:15:08.000Z","msg":"推波仔 劏外星人"},{"pid":"9222a39a64bb3c19577196cbbbce5bd6a7e8255c","tid":1738674,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d99f128de7e5b18c16d5e3209296f6c20146047","tid":1738674,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"逆權運動抗爭激烈，香港人反紅媒情緒高漲，遭網民譏諷為CCTVB的無綫，今日踏入52周年，惟有網民發起「全民和你賀台㷫」，有傳大台擔心被圍，所以將今晚舉行《珍惜香港 發放娛樂 TVB 52年》台慶直播節目，改為於昨日提早錄影，今日電視城變了「空城」！<br />\n<br />\n據知，聽聞今日除了《愛．回家之開心速遞》的劇組之外，所有演員都不用返電視城開工，而台慶的錄影廠空無一人，只餘下一個主景舞台，其他佈景板已全部拆除，只有一個52周年台慶蛋糕孤伶伶在台上，旁邊的化妝間都沒有人，連工作人員都沒有，整個電視城靜過鬼。<br />\n今晚台慶的司儀是汪明荃（阿姐）、鄭裕玲、陳貝兒、袁文傑、陸浩明等，阿姐回覆傳媒承認昨晚已錄影，今日不用做直播，所以阿姐不會返電視城。<br />\n<br />\n至於今晚的節目環節，包括有高海寧表演地上絲帶舞、王君馨表演鋼管舞、張曦雯表演空中瑜伽舞、周柏豪和菊梓喬合唱等，全部昨日已錄影，安排今晚播出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191119/large/1574155882_e4a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191119%2Flarge%2F1574155882_e4a5.jpg&h=55a7d5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191119/60285532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60285532&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=a411d6b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60285532&h=16c93f48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191119/60285532</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"各位手足，關於送林奠去大灣區的partition，尋日激增20000幾人(差不多簽署人數的10%)!，證明大家都好希望將佢舉家永遠封印晌大灣區！<br />\n<br />\n嘅然係咁就唔好停了，跟據早前民意調查有7成人唔妥佢嘅，咁我地嘅目標係咪應該set晌490萬個簽名呢？<br />\n<br />\n小弟英文唔好，如果可以的話，亦希望各手足可以幫手將佢推上國際！<br />\n<br />\n唔使俾錢架，簽完再share就唔使比錢㗎啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">最新消息：今朝22萬9千了！目標：490萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship?cs_tk=AtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%3D&amp;utm_campaign=514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=recruit_sign_digest&amp;utm_term=cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship%3Fcs_tk%3DAtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%253D%26utm_campaign%3D514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Drecruit_sign_digest%26utm_term%3Dcs&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=2ab04968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship?cs_tk=AtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%3D&amp;utm_campaign=514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=recruit_sign_digest&amp;utm_term=cs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hs8wPcW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHs8wPcW.jpg&h=66458b29&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}